g.text: Staging Deployment CI/CD Pipeline via Argo Workflows State Diagram
System is idle, waiting for actions
PR created, waiting for workflow start
GitHub Actions running unit tests (triggered by Argo Workflows)
GitHub Actions running integration tests (triggered by Argo Workflows)
Developer starts workflow with environment name input
Argo Workflows triggers PR policy check
Developer resolves issues and retries workflow
Argo Workflows triggers GitHub Actions to run unit tests
Unit tests pass, trigger integration tests
Argo Workflows triggers GitHub Actions to publish Docker image
